22
00:02:26,311 --> 00:02:27,800
Are you sure this is the place?

23
00:02:27,919 --> 00:02:28,800
Of course.

24
00:02:28,911 --> 00:02:29,590
According to...

25
00:02:29,599 --> 00:02:30,400
Stand properly.

26
00:02:32,520 --> 00:02:34,439
According to a reliable insider,

27
00:02:34,439 --> 00:02:37,719
Mr. Jing will be here today
discussing a cultural collaboration.

28
00:02:38,280 --> 00:02:39,879
But I've never seen him before.

29
00:02:40,439 --> 00:02:42,080
I did.

30
00:02:42,280 --> 00:02:43,439
Come, I'll take you to him.

31
00:02:46,400 --> 00:02:47,479
He's that man in black.

32
00:02:48,879 --> 00:02:49,680
Mr. Jing.

33
00:02:53,039 --> 00:02:54,199
Aren't you Mr. Xingchen

34
00:02:54,479 --> 00:02:55,479
