I'm now the secretary to GL's CEO.

38
00:03:02,280 --> 00:03:03,159
This is my boss.

39
00:03:04,599 --> 00:03:06,319
Hello, pardon me for coming uninvited.

40
00:03:06,319 --> 00:03:07,240
I'm Gu Liusu.

41
00:03:07,719 --> 00:03:08,639
Hello, Ms. Gu.

42
