123
00:07:09,399 --> 00:07:10,360
Xiaolu told me

124
00:07:10,360 --> 00:07:12,560
that you've put
the Starry Sea project aside.

125
00:07:14,480 --> 00:07:15,279
Why?

126
00:07:18,800 --> 00:07:20,800
Ten years ago, I met a female journalist

127
00:07:20,800 --> 00:07:22,279
during my field trip abroad.

128
00:07:22,519 --> 00:07:23,800
We clicked instantly

129
00:07:23,800 --> 00:07:24,959
and became good friends.

130
00:07:25,800 --> 00:07:27,560
Later, war broke out in her country.

131
00:07:27,560 --> 00:07:28,800
She went to the front line.

132
00:07:29,639 --> 00:07:30,639
In her,

133
00:07:31,240 --> 00:07:33,160
I saw how cruel war really was.

134
00:07:33,439 --> 00:07:35,240
So I wove feathers symbolizing peace

135
00:07:35,240 --> 00:07:36,519
into an olive branch

136
00:07:36,920 --> 00:07:38,360
and came up with the Starry Sea.

137
00:07:39,040 --> 00:07:40,680
Both of us thought this design

138
00:07:41,079 --> 00:07:42,639
truly expressed our vision.

139
00:07:44,040 --> 00:07:45,079
That sounds meaningful.

140
00:07:45,800 --> 00:07:47,240
Then why did you stop working on it?

141
00:07:53,079 --> 00:07:54,720
Because she died on the front line.

142
00:08:01,519 --> 00:08:02,360
So...

143
00:08:05,720 --> 00:08:07,519
