in the diamond industry.

153
00:08:47,466 --> 00:08:48,750
I really can't see through you.

154
00:08:51,440 --> 00:08:53,039
Do what you can first.

155
00:08:53,360 --> 00:08:54,840
Then do what you want.

156
00:08:55,639 --> 00:08:57,840
The former makes my livelihood.

157
00:08:59,159 --> 00:09:01,200
The latter keeps me hopeful.

158
00:09:11,919 --> 00:09:13,159
Gu Liusu!

159
00:09:13,759 --> 00:09:16,080
Even if I can't enter your utopia,

160
00:09:16,279 --> 00:09:19,360
I can feel you want it to be beautiful!

161
00:09:30,440 --> 00:09:33,080
What does the Starry Sea
in your heart look like?

162
00:09:34,360 --> 00:09:37,519
Just pass the beauty in your heart on.

163
00:09:50,644 --> 00:09:51,955
Shall we go horseback riding?

164
00:09:52,822 --> 00:09:55,630
